{"prompt": "Generate a website for a edtech platform. The website should be sleek and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EduTech Platform</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #007bff;\n            --secondary-blue: #e7f3ff;\n            --text-dark: #333333;\n            --text-light: #ffffff;\n            --accent-color: #0056b3;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            color: var(--text-dark);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .logo {\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: var(--text-light);\n        }\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 2rem;\n        }\n        nav ul li a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            font-weight: 500;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n        .hero-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-blue) 0%, #0056b3 100%);\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 5rem 2rem;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            min-height: 60vh;\n        }\n        .hero-section h1 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            max-width: 800px;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #004085;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n        .features-section {\n            padding: 4rem 2rem;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .features-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n        .features-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .feature-card {\n            background-color: var(--text-light);\n            padding: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        .feature-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .feature-card i {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n        .feature-card h3 {\n            font-size: 1.4rem;\n            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n        .feature-card p {\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            margin-top: 4rem;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"logo\">EduTech Pro</a>\n        <nav>\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#\">Home</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#\">Courses</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#\">About</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n        <h1>Unlock Your Potential with Smart Learning</h1>\n        <p>\n            Experience a revolutionary way to learn with our cutting-edge educational technology platform.\n            Access expert-led courses, interactive lessons, and personalized learning paths.\n        </p>\n        <button class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</button>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"features-section\">\n        <h2>Why Choose EduTech Pro?</h2>\n        <div class=\"features-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chalkboard-teacher\"></i>\n                <h3>Expert Instructors</h3>\n                <p>Learn from industry leaders and seasoned educators.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-graduation-cap\"></i>\n                <h3>Diverse Courses</h3>\n                <p>A wide range of subjects and skill levels available.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                <h3>Innovative Learning</h3>\n                <p>Engage with interactive content and real-world applications.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                <h3>Personalized Paths</h3>\n                <p>Tailored learning journeys to meet your goals.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 EduTech Pro. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}